snippet.title: Amber Gibson’s brother Connor Gibson was charged as his sister’s murdered.
snippet.description:
Amber Gibson’s brother was charged with murder and sexual assault as a result of his sister’s death.
Connor Gibson, 19, was likewise blamed for rape and endeavoring to distort the course of equity by investigators.  The short private hearing at Hamilton Sheriff Court came five days after his kin, 16, was found dead in the forest close to the town's Cazdow Glen.
